## endgood.directive.js

**Summary:** Directive (element: "endGoodCancel") showing the successful neutral-rating result after cancellation. Displays role-specific text (donor sees "offering still available", applicant sees "no longer reserved") and provides buttons to select a new user or close.

**Dependencies:**
- app/app/calification/calification.module.js — registered on calification module

**Tags:** calification, rating, cancelled, directive, ui

**Implementation:** app/app/calification/cancelled/endGood/endgood.directive.js
